" title=\"Amour-propre\">Amour-propre</a></i></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/General_will\" title=\"General will\">General will</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<div role=\"navigation\" class=\"navbox\" aria-labelledby=\"Pygmalion_from_Ovid&amp;#039;s_Metamorphoses\" style=\"padding:3px\"><table class=\"nowraplinks collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;color:inherit\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist navbar mini\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/wiki/Template:Pygmalion_navbox\" title=\"Template:Pygmalion navbox\"><abbr title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;-moz-box-shadow:none;-webkit-box-shadow:none;box-shadow:none; padding:0;\">v</abbr></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/wiki/Template_talk:Pygmalion_navbox\" title=\"Template talk:Pygmalion navbox\"><abbr title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;-moz-box-shadow:none;-webkit-box-shadow:none;box-shadow:none; padding:0;\">t</abbr></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Pygmalion_navbox&amp;action=edit\"><abbr title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;-moz-box-shadow:none;-webkit-box-shadow:none;box-shadow:none; padding:0;\">e</abbr></a></li></ul></div><div id=\"Pygmalion_from_Ovid&amp;#039;s_Metamorphoses\" style=\"font-size:114%;margin:0 4em\"><i><a href=\"/wiki/Pygmalion_(mythology)\" title=\"Pygmalion (mythology)\">Pygmalion</a></i> from <a href=\"/wiki/Ovid\" title=\"Ovid\">Ovid</a>'s <i><a href=\"/wiki/Metamorphoses\" title=\"Metamorphoses\">Metamorphoses</a></i></div></th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">Characters</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Galatea_(mythology)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Galatea (mythology)\">Galatea</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Propoetides\" title=\"Propoetides\">Propoetides</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">Opera</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-even hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Pigmalion_(opera)\" title=\"Pigmalion (opera)\">Pigmalion</a></i> (1748)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Pygmalion_(opera)\" title=\"Pygmalion (opera)\">Pygmalion</a></i> (1779)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Pimmalione\" title=\"Pimmalione\">Pimmalione</a></i> (1809)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Il_Pigmalione\" title=\"Il Pigmalione\">Il Pigmalione</a></i> (1816)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Die_sch%C3%B6ne_Galath%C3%A9e\" title=\"Die sch\u00f6ne Galath\u00e9e\">Die sch\u00f6ne Galath\u00e9e</a></i> (1863 operetta)</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">Ballet</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Pygmalion,_ou_La_Statue_de_Chypre\" title=\"Pygmalion, ou La Statue de Chypre\">Pygmalion, ou La Statue de Chypre</a></i></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">Play</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-even hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><i><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pygmalion</a></i> (1762)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Pygmalion_and_Galatea_(play)\" title=\"Pygmalion and Galatea (play)\">Pygmalion and Galatea</a></i> (1871)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Pygmalion_(play)\"